1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 21=

4
00:00:27,239 --> 00:00:30,440
Mr. Peng, it's only been a few days.

5
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:33,600
You're looking even more handsome.

6
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:38,840
I like you more every time I see you.

7
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:40,399
Like me that much?

8
00:00:40,799 --> 00:00:42,520
Then how about dying by my blade?

9
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:44,439
Brat,

10
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:46,359
I'll turn you into

11
00:00:46,359 --> 00:00:47,799
my finest corpse puppet.

12
00:00:47,799 --> 00:00:51,520
Let's see
if you can still talk tough then.

13
00:00:53,479 --> 00:00:56,920
You old hag! I'll kill you today

14
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,399
and avenge my master.

15
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:02,679
You little brat.

16
00:01:02,679 --> 00:01:04,000
You talk big.

17
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:06,000
Your master was much more obedient

18
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:08,560
when he knelt before Master

19
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:10,920
and begged for his life.

20
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,120
Die!

21
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,159
Where's the Luocha Blade Demon?

22
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,760
Tell him to come out and die!

23
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,280
This manor is creepy.

24
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:33,599
We've been walking forever
and haven't seen a soul.

25
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:35,079
Of course we haven't.

26
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:36,799
I told you to use the front gate,

27
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:37,480
but you refused.

28
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,519
You insisted on
taking the back entrance.

29
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,879
Now we're lost.

30
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:40,640
Happy?

31
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,760
What are you talking about?

32
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,680
Walking in through the front gate
would've drawn too much attention.

33
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,560
The Demon Sect isn't blind.

34
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:47,799
We would've walked
straight into their trap.

35
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:50,480
Well, you've got it all figured out,
Mr. Tang.

36
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,400
Then why don't you tell us

37
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,680
what we should do now?

38
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,120
Our best option

39
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:56,200
is to split up.

40
00:01:58,879 --> 00:02:00,200
If anyone finds anything strange,

41
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:02,159
whistle three times.

42
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:04,000
Just be careful.

43
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,480
If you find anything...

44
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,240
Ziting!

45
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,400
Ziting!

46
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:14,280
Ziting.

47
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:15,159
Ziting.

48
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,080
Ms. Duan!

49
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,479
You think you can beat me?

50
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:39,319
Even your master

51
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,599
knelt before us

52
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:42,479
and begged us to spare

53
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:44,039
the Wudu Sect before he died.

54
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:47,800
He looked utterly pathetic.

55
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,199
I'll kill you!

56
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:58,719
Your master fell victim to
my Bone-Eroding Poison.

57
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:01,560
I watched him roll around

58
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,639
on the ground in agony.

59
00:03:03,639 --> 00:03:05,080
My venomous parasites

60
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,240
ate through his organs

61
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:09,800
until they were nothing but blood.

62
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:12,960
Before he died, he kept begging me,

63
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,879
"Spare Qingyao! Spare Qingyao!"

64
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:17,000
How pitiful.

65
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:24,919
(Qingyao,)

66
00:03:25,599 --> 00:03:26,439
(if anything happens to me)

67
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:27,719
(on this journey,)

68
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,680
(protect the Wudu Sect.)

69
00:03:29,919 --> 00:03:32,120
(Protect our home.)

70
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,639
(Qingyao,)

71
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:36,039
(when you face a powerful enemy,
keep a clear head.)

72
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,919
(That's how you'll survive
when all seems lost.)

73
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:41,280
I'll send you to him today.

74
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,680
You...

75
00:03:58,319 --> 00:04:00,120
You broke through?

76
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,319
Thanks to you, I broke through

77
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,479
to the fourth rank.

78
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:08,120
This strike is for my master.

79
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,319
And this

80
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,319
is for

81
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:18,920
the Wudu Sect disciples you killed.

82
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,800
And this one is for

83
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:25,639
the countless martial heroes

84
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:28,079
the Demon Sect has killed.

85
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,600
Master,

86
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:40,240
I've avenged you.

87
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:56,319
You finally showed yourself.

88
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:59,920
So a woman died.

89
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,480
Hardly worth mentioning.

90
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:04,319
That girl had more backbone
than I expected.

91
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:06,600
Even at death's door,
she was still protecting you.

92
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:08,800
Too bad she chose the wrong man.

93
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,120
She was dead the moment she chose you.

94
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,199
I'll tear you

95
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:18,079
limb from limb!

96
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:29,900
(Sansi Hall)

97
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,600
Sansi Hall?

98
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:04,240
That's strange. Where did she go?

99
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:18,879
Could this path lead
to the Demon Sect's sacred altar?

100
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,800
I'm a genius.

101
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:44,000
Master,
everything is just as you expected.

102
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,600
Peng Dasheng is locked in battle

103
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,839
with the Luocha Blade Demon.

104
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:50,319
Then take another guess.

105
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,000
Who do you think will win?

106
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,759
I wouldn't presume to guess.

107
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,839
Go ahead.

108
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,720
You won't be punished.

109
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:04,639
I think... Peng Dasheng will win.

110
00:07:04,959 --> 00:07:05,839
Why?

111
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:09,040
Master, if you wanted Peng Dasheng dead,

112
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,560
you could kill him with ease.

113
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:14,439
You even set this elaborate trap
at Liuchu Manor.

114
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,560
Your plan must go far beyond

115
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,560
killing just one man.

116
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:20,439
So I suspect

117
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:23,720
Peng Dasheng

118
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:26,959
is worth more to you alive.

119
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:33,399
I'm glad

120
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,360
you understand that much.

121
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:39,439
But when did I say

122
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:41,639
I was letting him live?

123
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,439
Master...

124
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:45,600
I...

125
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:52,759
Su Yeye,
don't forget who gave you your life.

126
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:56,319
Everything I have
comes from you, Master.

127
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:58,839
Even giving my life
wouldn't begin to repay you.

128
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:03,240
Then how dare you fall
for that boy behind my back?

129
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,439
I... I didn't.

130
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,560
You didn't?

131
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,759
In that flower carriage,

132
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,560
you were flirting with him.

133
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,120
Did you think I was blind?

134
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:18,720
I... I only did it

135
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:20,199
for you, Master.

136
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,720
For me?

137
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:26,240
If I hadn't played the part
of the top courtesan that day,

138
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:29,000
people would've grown suspicious
of Zhenqu Pavilion.

139
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,560
I only played along

140
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:34,039
to keep them from catching on

141
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,399
and protect your plan.

142
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,639
It wasn't what I wanted.

143
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,039
If you still blame me, Master,

144
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,320
I'll...

145
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:45,240
I'll take my own life to make amends.

146
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,320
Enough.

147
00:08:50,639 --> 00:08:52,519
That's my buddy!

148
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:55,840
He even won over
Su Yeye, the top courtesan.

149
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:58,240
What a lucky guy.

150
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:06,039
Who dares enter my sacred altar?

151
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,519
Sorry. Wrong turn.

152
00:09:08,519 --> 00:09:09,240
Don't mind me.

153
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,759
Carry on. Go on, keep talking.

154
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:14,320
Pretty boy!

155
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:14,759
Run!

156
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:23,399
You two weaklings dared spy on me?

157
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:28,919
Don't bother chasing them.

158
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:32,639
The Corpse Miasma Pool below
was formed from my baleful energy.

159
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,919
Neither of them will make it out alive.

160
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:38,440
Come with me.
Let's see what's going on outside.

161
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,519
Yes, Master.

162
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:48,600
Are you all right?

163
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,639
I've got luck on my side.

164
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:50,440
I won't die that easily.

165
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:56,039
Unless I'm mistaken,

166
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:58,039
this miasma was formed
from baleful energy.

167
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:59,039
Touch it, and you're dead.

168
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:01,440
It's just miasma.

169
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:03,039
Don't make such a fuss.

170
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,639
Watch out!

171
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,320
That's Corpse Miasma Hellfire.

172
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,879
Once it touches you,
it seeps into your flesh.

173
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:28,519
It burns bone and soul.

174
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:29,399
It can never be extinguished.

175
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:30,919
That's terrifying.

176
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:34,960
Have you noticed?

177
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:38,080
The miasma's closing in on us.

178
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,080
Whoa.

179
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:42,320
It really is.

180
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,440
With cultivation that weak,

181
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,759
you dare trade blows with me?

182
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:04,399
You think they call me
the Luocha Blade Demon

183
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:04,919
for nothing?

184
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:06,600
I don't care who you are!

185
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,360
All I know is

186
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,000
I'm going to kill you

187
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:13,000
today.

188
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:17,039
It's only been a few days, boy,

189
00:11:17,039 --> 00:11:18,440
and your blade skills
have improved quite a bit.

190
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:19,840
In that case,

191
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,240
let me show you

192
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,879
the true way of the blade.

193
00:11:59,879 --> 00:12:01,159
No one has ever survived

194
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:03,039
my Three Luocha Strikes.

195
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:05,399
Your eight extraordinary meridians
are severed.

196
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:08,679
You have at most two hours left.

197
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:14,080
So your genuine qi is gone too, right?

198
00:12:35,799 --> 00:12:36,600
No...

199
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:37,639
Impossible!

200
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:40,080
I severed those meridians myself!

201
00:12:40,940 --> 00:12:43,420
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

202
00:12:43,420 --> 00:12:47,500
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

203
00:12:48,799 --> 00:12:51,039
H-Heaven's Gate Shines Upon the World...

204
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:53,799
If you hadn't forced me
to swallow the soul jade,

205
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:56,480
I never would've absorbed
its spiritual power.

206
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,440
You actually refined the soul jade?

207
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:08,900
♪Come on♪

208
00:13:12,420 --> 00:13:14,100
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

209
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:19,020
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

210
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:22,220
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

211
00:13:22,460 --> 00:13:25,300
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

212
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:28,300
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

213
00:13:28,820 --> 00:13:31,780
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

214
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:35,020
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

215
00:13:35,180 --> 00:13:38,100
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

216
00:13:38,260 --> 00:13:41,020
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

217
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:44,900
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

218
00:13:44,940 --> 00:13:47,940
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

219
00:13:47,980 --> 00:13:53,620
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

220
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:56,060
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

221
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:59,140
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

222
00:13:59,860 --> 00:14:02,260
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

223
00:14:02,380 --> 00:14:06,060
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

224
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:08,780
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

225
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:11,820
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

226
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:15,260
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

227
00:14:15,300 --> 00:14:19,580
♪I am my own king♪

228
00:14:32,660 --> 00:14:34,220
♪I emerge into the world♪

229
00:14:34,220 --> 00:14:35,980
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

230
00:14:35,980 --> 00:14:37,340
♪My pride is my trump card♪

231
00:14:37,340 --> 00:14:39,140
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

232
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:40,540
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

233
00:14:40,540 --> 00:14:42,300
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

234
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,820
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

235
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:45,540
♪I dare to break every rule♪

236
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:46,860
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

237
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:48,700
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

238
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:49,940
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

239
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:52,180
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

240
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:53,700
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

241
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:55,300
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

242
00:14:55,300 --> 00:14:56,900
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

243
00:14:56,900 --> 00:14:58,620
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

244
00:14:58,620 --> 00:15:00,340
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

245
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:01,700
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

246
00:15:01,700 --> 00:15:03,340
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

247
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:04,820
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

248
00:15:04,820 --> 00:15:06,540
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

249
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:08,140
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

250
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:09,700
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

251
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:14,020
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

252
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:16,180
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

253
00:15:16,180 --> 00:15:18,780
♪Let me write the legend♪

254
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:26,220
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

255
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:29,540
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

256
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:32,020
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

257
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:36,100
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

258
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:39,060
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

259
00:15:39,180 --> 00:15:41,540
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

260
00:15:41,540 --> 00:15:44,580
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

261
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:49,620
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
